comments: He\'s a really nice teacher and he explains very well, even though he can get a little off topic but he makes his lectures interesting, fun,and informative. In addition he\'s a really cute teacher!!!:)
I just finished his intro to Philosophy class. I must say, Ian is an amazing professor. One of the best classes I\'ve ever taken.
Great teacher. If you\'re taking intro logic or intro philosophy he\'s the one to take. had him for both. can sometimes be vague in what he expects at first but it becomes clear and he is consistent.
